# The Paheko app comes from `COPY --from` the official image, not the build
# context. All we need from the context is modules/ and config.local.php, so
# ignore everything and allowlist those two.
#
# (An allowlist is safe here only because we no longer `ADD <git-url>`: buildah
# applies .dockerignore to an ADD-pulled tree too, so a `*` would silently wipe
# it — and only locally, since BuildKit/CI doesn't filter ADD. Reintroducing an
# ADD-git line would mean switching this back to an anchored blocklist.)
*
!modules
!config.local.php
